{"tid":374228,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想乞食一定揀IT","createTime":"2017-08-25T14:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T16:28:24.000Z","uid":85271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca64d18ca8e411116877aeaa500d6731693e41e","tid":374228,"uid":85271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"又有機構裁減資訊科技（IT）員工！《路透社》引述兩名消息人士報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">保險公司AXA安盛在港裁250人，全部均是IT員工，原因是削減成本，而香港原本是AXA亞洲區的IT總部。</span><br />\n<br />\n裁員行動在本周四發生，AXA並同時移師至菲律賓馬尼拉及馬來西亞吉隆坡，在兩處設立資訊科技中心，分別聘請300人及110人，並形容在這些地區設立IT部是「在可負擔的成本上增強部門效能」。<br />\n<br />\nAXA發言人並無確認或否認裁員一事，僅指出AXA恒常地審視業務，以提升產品種類及服務，並於亞洲建立科技平台，致力提升科技水平及效能，中間或會牽涉部分區域的人手重整。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指出，不少企業因應減省成本，加上香港人工貴，租金貴，故此一些工序由其他地區取代，不過他認為，大企業在裁員前，必須要慎重考慮是否有其他安排，例如內部轉職，否則對其形象並不好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">今年IT人被企業開刀屬等閒事，例如國泰航空今年5月裁190名經理級以上員工，IT部是重災區，人數多達77人，主要是削減成本考慮。滙豐今年3月有逾百名IT員工收「大信封」，當時發言人回應指，削減成本為該行策略一部份，以確保競爭力及維持運作效率。</span><br />\n<br />\nAXA亦於2014年以26億元作價，將香港強積金業務轉售予美國信安，不過當時並未有牽涉裁員。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&d=J7JE%2FUvgVmiymhQ0sLk4gwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=089a0991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&h=065e9153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c794a5f6a596affdce909384b9101a9d29f8e92a","tid":374228,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"axa有無保險保it狗唔俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9840750efebf36ff9dec9632b62587d664cd3e73","tid":374228,"uid":132578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"不論有冇能力都唔做IT"},{"pid":"830926195f38ebdc3015b63a025afa464e54f9e1","tid":374228,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"問過DESIGN未"},{"pid":"cfc87a01952e550f0549c7d62f95b9f96555c008","tid":374228,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c7da854944991da7a8add5d606a741cc466338b","tid":374228,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問過DESIGN未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港真心中意而做design嘅人太少<br />\n抵佢地乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}